article.headline: Small scores 15 as Army knocks off Lehigh 68-57

images.name: Army Black Knights vs. Lehigh Mountain Hawks: Game Highlights
images.caption: Army Black Knights vs. Lehigh Mountain Hawks: Game Highlights

article.linkText: Small scores 15 as Army knocks off Lehigh 68-57
article.story: BETHLEHEM, Pa. -- — TJ Small's 15 points helped Army defeat Lehigh 68-57 on Wednesday night. Small added six rebounds for the Black Knights (7-17, 3-8 Patriot League). Ryan Curry scored 11 points and added five rebounds. Josh Scovens shot 4 for 12, including 1 for 5 from beyond the arc to finish with 11 points. The Mountain Hawks (7-15, 4-7) were led in scoring by Dominic Parolin, who finished with 13 points and two blocks. Tyler Whitney-Sidney added 12 points for Lehigh. In addition, Bube Momah finished with nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
